import React from 'react'; import './Light.css'; import { useEffect, useRef } from 'react'; import Chart from 'chart.js'; import Flatpickr from 'react-flatpickr'; import 'flatpickr/dist/themes/material_blue.css'; import { registerables } from 'chart.js'; function Dashboard() { const lineChartRef = useRef(null); const pieChartRef = useRef(null); const barChartRef = useRef(null); const barChartTwoRef = useRef(null); const [date, setDate] = React.useState(new Date()); useEffect(() => { // Line Chart const ctxLine = lineChartRef.current.getContext('2d'); const gradient = ctxLine.createLinearGradient(0, 0, 0, 225); gradient.addColorStop(0, 'rgba(215, 227, 244, 1)'); gradient.addColorStop(1, 'rgba(215, 227, 244, 0)'); new Chart(ctxLine, { type: 'line', data: { labels: ['Jan', 'Feb', 'Mar', 'Apr', 'May', 'Jun', 'Jul', 'Aug', 'Sep', 'Oct', 'Nov', 'Dec'], datasets: [{ label: 'Pass (%)', fill: true, backgroundColor: gradient, borderColor: '#007bff', // Equivalent to window.theme.primary data: [40, 60, 75, 85, 90, 99, 100, 92, 94, 98, 90, 82] }] }, options: { maintainAspectRatio: false, legend: { display: false }, scales: { xAxes: [{ reverse: true, gridLines: { color: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.0)' } }], yAxes: [{ ticks: { stepSize: 1000 }, gridLines: { color: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.0)' } }] } } }); // Pie Chart const ctxPie = pieChartRef.current.getContext('2d'); new Chart(ctxPie, { type: 'pie', data: { labels: ['Azure Cloud', 'Php', 'Dynamics'], datasets: [{ data: [205, 201, 99], backgroundColor: ['#007bff', '#ffc107', '#dc3545'], // Equivalent to window.theme.primary, warning, danger borderWidth: 5 }] }, options: { responsive: true, maintainAspectRatio: false, legend: { display: false }, cutoutPercentage: 75 } }); // Bar Chart 1 const ctxBar = barChartRef.current.getContext('2d'); new Chart(ctxBar, { type: 'bar', data: { labels: ['Jan', 'Feb', 'Mar', 'Apr', 'May', 'Jun', 'Jul', 'Aug', 'Sep', 'Oct', 'Nov', 'Dec'], datasets: [{ label: 'Users', backgroundColor: '#007bff', borderColor: '#007bff', data: [54, 67, 41, 55, 62, 45, 55, 73, 60, 76, 48, 79], barPercentage: 0.75, categoryPercentage: 0.5 }] }, options: { maintainAspectRatio: false, legend: { display: false }, scales: { yAxes: [{ ticks: { stepSize: 20 }, gridLines: { display: false } }], xAxes: [{ gridLines: { color: 'transparent' } }] } } }); // Bar Chart 2 const ctxBarTwo = barChartTwoRef.current.getContext('2d'); new Chart(ctxBarTwo, { type: 'bar', data: { labels: ['Jan', 'Feb', 'Mar', 'Apr', 'May', 'Jun', 'Jul', 'Aug', 'Sep', 'Oct', 'Nov', 'Dec'], datasets: [ { label: 'Pass', backgroundColor: '#007bff', borderColor: '#007bff', data: [54, 67, 41, 55, 62, 45, 55, 73, 60, 76, 48, 79], barPercentage: 0.75, categoryPercentage: 0.5 }, { label: 'Fail', backgroundColor: '#dee2e6', borderColor: '#dee2e6', data: [20, 6, 24, 48, 10, 15, 30, 28, 18, 22, 33, 40], barPercentage: 0.75, categoryPercentage: 0.5 } ] }, options: { maintainAspectRatio: false, legend: { display: false }, scales: { yAxes: [{ ticks: { stepSize: 20 }, gridLines: { display: false } }], xAxes: [{ gridLines: { color: 'transparent' } }] } } }); }, []); return (
